    "rich_text_QVGMph": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_FMLAb9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "THE SHIRT THAT STARTED IT ALL",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h2",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_MyWtr8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The shirt that launched the brand has been completely revamped<br/>for to take on even more rod-bending, pulse-raising moments. The new, upgraded version features a full back panel of moisture-wicking mesh that enhances breathability and shortens dry time. To keep you out on the water longer, the Icon provides 50+ UPF rating and is made with I.C.E. (Internal Cooling Element) technology. This incredible fiber-technology reacts to sweat by producing an endothermic reaction to lower body temperature. The raglan sleeve cut provides full range of motion to eliminate pulls and bunching while casting, and it's antimicrobial treatment will help keep you from smelling like your catch when you dock up at the local watering hole for a post trip celebratory brew.</p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "button_meAzTd": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link_label": "Shop Mens",
            "link": "shopify://collections/mens-icon-collection"
          }
        },
