      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Icon-Hot-Spot-SS25.jpg",
        "heading": "The Shirt that started it all",
        "marker_style": "style1",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "description": "<p>Tested and perfected for over 10 years on the water. The sun is not your friend—sweat in the eyes, a scorched neck, and a battle over the last icy Modelo, doesn’t add up to a great day on the water. Avoid the sun's perils, and stay out longer with our best-selling performance top.</p>",
