        },
        "heading_7wdVaG": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "NEW ICON BOTTOMS",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h2",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_6zjNdk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To keep you protected from head to toe, we've launched our Icon Pants and Icon Shorts to perfectly complement to our signature top. We love this 4-way stretch nylon for one key reason - long wear durability. Built and tested in partnership with our Pros and Captains who pay their bills on a boat, the feature set is dialed in for ultimate versatility. Lightweight ... breathable ... quick dry ... 50+ UPF protection .... add in DWR coating to shed spray and light rain, stain resistant treatment, and details for a custom fit, and a built-in reinforced plier pocket and you have the ultimate bottom for fishing hard.</p>",
            "size": "text-size-large"
          }
        },
        "button_f8VebW": {
